cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this code, please cite the main paper (the preferred citation below) — not the software entry or any Web Appendix supplement."
title: "Cross-Fitted Survey-Weighted TMLE with Design-Based Variance for Causal Machine Learning"
abstract: >-
  Reference implementation and reproducible analysis code for a cross-fitted,
  survey-weighted Targeted Maximum Likelihood Estimator (TMLE) of the population
  average treatment effect, with a design-based (Taylor-series-linearization)
  variance for stratified multistage survey samples.
type: software
authors:
